Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙手抱頭！ 退後！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是403號吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要賭一把嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭她能夠逃多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只能順著管道跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是逃不出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 會走的更遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那個傢伙的話 絕對！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SB們！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢追老娘的屁股！ 做好覺悟了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代價可不便宜哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,403號 Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果無意投降 就將你當場擊斃

Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\pos(1287,609)\c&HFFFFFD&}再見了！無情的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.87,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(190,894)\c&H2EE2F9&}      三月10日 橘子鎮(Laranja)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三月10日 晴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清晨6時起床 我最早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}越獄事件發生已經過了一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:04:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}從重兵把守、被譽為不可能逃脫的 Diamandra重刑犯特別監獄逃脫的是囚犯michiko malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}乘著昨夜的狂風天氣 隱藏行蹤 至今仍未被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個只有我是外人的家 這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包飯 低鹽量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋殼掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點焦味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro神父和他的妻子Johanna
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹頭徹尾的虛假父母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 討厭 這個孩子在欺瞞我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana 不要成為隱藏失敗的不成器的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣冠冕堂皇地讓我重做蛋包飯 這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maria姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maria 這個名字有點問題(一點不像聖母)...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.40,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Gabriel:大天使之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gabriel弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Belenbauza Yamada家的諸位成員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、Hana的一天就這樣開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要為妻子和孩子們的健康向主表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大體上(早餐)就這樣結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H69F2FB&\fs72\pos(1430,1013)}土豆鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.28,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}鼻屎＝鼻（はな/Hana）くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 鼻屎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這往下是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就在海裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去撿！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水裏面是走不起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水裏能呼吸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些黑斑到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水桶的水被我弄翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道值多少錢嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為自己是小孩子就會被原諒 在我這裏是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴巾是用來擦身體的 不是用來穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抓了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事情天天發生 看不到盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 利索點！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則打你個腦門開花、血漿四濺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:39.39,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Banco Do Brasil:巴西銀行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三月15日 今天政府的人會來察看我的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只是來看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下錢就走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.90,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(200,200)\pos(115,1035)\c&H83E8FA&}圣佩德羅教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana 我將這些贈與你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.87,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ciencia:科學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana 還記得今天早晨的新聞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏 像你這樣的孩子不出賣身體或內臟就無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你從水深火熱之中拯救出來的是誰？ 你明白吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是... 主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是... 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:26.96,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}語出新約馬太福音5:43 原文"Ye have heard that it hath been said,Thou shalt love thy neighbour,and hate thine enemy."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要有怨恨 "愛你的鄰居"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人剛剛收買了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Maria的舊書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:40.30,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}在巴拉伊鎮發生銀行搶劫的新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:49.51,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}犯人是日前從Diamandra重刑犯特別監獄逃跑的 Michiko Malandro可能性非常高...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去很舒服啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價格很貴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是信徒的佈施 談不上什麼價格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像過得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸甚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道"Debody of the year"嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是什麼 debo... dy？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅頒發給作出傑出貢獻的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老公被選中了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個叫Gonzalez的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是非常棘手的壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我老公一番佈道就把他馴服了 現在他可是優秀的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.46,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a7\pos(1383,50)\c&H714B1A&}五個月前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gonzalez是因為腦子裏還殘留著子彈才會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gonzalez 主說已經原諒了你的所有作為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是野貓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個 是Maria撿回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對它真的是很疼愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blanco在大便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想點辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧Blanco的事情能不能換人 早晨開始我就頭暈的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是誰值日？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有增加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道養一個孩子要花多少錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 討厭 好髒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個給我扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.10,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(190,1038)\c&H2BEFEF&}  三月16日 Belenbauza家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blanco在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 說起來早上沒有看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨晚起就沒有看見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana 你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我看見你把它帶出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶到哪里去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blanco的速度更快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blanco二世
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你不覺得髒嗎？ 這只Blanco
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好髒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了Gabriel 我有好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blanco是白色的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須弄乾淨些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 馴馬 馴馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 給我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒做！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我作對是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你給我滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們家也不需要像你這樣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直在忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被耍來耍去 知道我在想什麼嗎！ 知道我在看什麼嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給老娘記住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:17:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為害怕一個人回去 本想帶Blanco一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從道路的遠處有人會來迎接我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Belen什麼的Yamada的家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是的... 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個叫Hana的小鬼在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明早我去接她 給我準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 您是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 好像是Hana的母親會來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她母親不是死了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妒忌我的地位的傢伙的伎倆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:31.07,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Certificado de adocao de menor:未成年人收養證書
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消減養育費讓我為難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把獵槍拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向這些傢伙反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:45.72,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a5\pos(217,31)\c&H36C0EC&}   三月17日 Belenbauza家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 開動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方把Hana藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你 四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎？ Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 一直盯著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半張著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:34.16,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}L.B.D.D.:葡萄牙語“自由”的縮寫(liberdade)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 別給我裝啞巴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰會來迎接我 我一直祈求著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三月17日的早晨 那個人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個人 到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}待續
